  <brief_title>TDM Guided Early Optimization of ADAL in Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Therapeutic Drug Monitoring Guided Early Optimization of Adalimumab in Crohn's Disease; A Randomized Open Label Study</official_title>
